        "rating": 5,
        "text": "This is by far the nicest pawn shop I've ever been to! The service is top notch.  All the crew are friendly & welcoming. The atmosphere is bright & clean, very well organized and everything is labeled clearly. They have a great layaway,  and very fair prices.  Everything they sell is well taken care of and clean, unlike most pawn shops. I definitely don't get the feeling of being \"shady\" like a lot of other shops. I never expected a pawn shop to feel like a regular store with great service, but Arizona's Finest Pawn Shop managed to do it!",
        "relative_time": "2 years ago",
        "publish_time": "2023-05-04T18:11:17.270470Z",
        "google_review_uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURSdTdQcXN3RRAB!2m1!1s0x872b6bf41ce85b17:0x61b3cdd27488f92a"
