        "rating": 5,
        "text": "Definitely my favorite pawn shop! Alicia and Vanessa were super helpful. I've been to so many pawn shops looking for jewelry, and a few other things. They were able to give me options and help me out with a layaway plan. 10/10 will definitely be back!",
