        "text": "I have been to to Arizonas  finest three times to pawn items! They made the process painless!! Quick, courteous and Painless!!! All three very important to me! Josh and team work amazingly well together very fluid and accurate!! In the event you find your self needing to pawn something , valuables, jewelry or a gun this is the place they give you fair prices and no hassle!! Corner of 83rd Ave and Peoria!! Arizonas  finest pawn shop! Right now 13 days for just 13%",
